MEXICO
Dong kingman, the award winning Chinese-American crtist, trowels the world sketching and painting
the beautiful, the monumental and the picturesque. His watercolors grace more than forty
permanent museum and private collections in the USA and abroad
Sunny Mexico, the Land of Enchantment, is a unique port of call. This country of great diversity can
boast of a beautiful and bustling capital in Mexico City- the oldest city in North America
Filled with plazas and wide boulevards, Mexico City's many historic and cultural landmarks make this
thriving economic center one of the most picturesque places in which to do business in the
Americas. Pan Am can take you to Mexico City from more than 20 US cities, and from just about
anywhere else in the world. Non-stop service to Miami, Tampa, and Houston is complimented
by one-stop service to New York, Washington, Los Angeles, San Francisco, New Orleans, London,
Frankfurt, Paris, Caracas, Rio de Janeiro and Buenos Aires to name but a few.
